{
  "stem": "5761.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And actually, I was the-- the commander, the general.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was nice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very good.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The whole family was respected from the gentile.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had a lot of non-gentile friends.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And-- and when I visited in 1989, in-- not sure-- they don't-- didn't recognize me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I was walking the streets and approaching older people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I kept asking them, do you remember the Feit family?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They kinda got excited.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Are they still alive?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the next question was, when are they coming back?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were very liked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So your family occupied a position of respect in the community.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, very much so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Both among the Jews and among the non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Matter of fact, my father was running also to be a senator in the Polish, you know, government.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had all the Polish people there, rich people, and which were very friendly-- very close to my father.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If anything had to be decided in the town, they never did without my father.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Things started to change actually, in 1938, when the rumors were about Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, they was thinking to-- to go into a war with Europe.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Polish people in town became anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To an extent it-- there were times there was a pogrom.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were just running in the streets and hitting Jews, breaking windows.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I can never forget that they were approaching our house, and my four older brothers came out the street when they were near our house.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They walked over to them and said, don't you dare do any damages.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Don't you try.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because we're gonna fight you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they just kept going.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But it was a very tense situation.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
